description = "A libretro emulation core for the Mattel Intellivision with onscreen interactive keypad overlays for Android (touchscreen), Windows, and Linux (mouse). Supports ROM-specific overlays (370x600 PNG files) placed in system/freeintv_overlays/. Many Intellivision games relied on controller overlays for context, and custom overlays can enhance gameplay. Features include traditional controller support, 12-button keypad input, and custom overlay graphics."
